{"tid":1066990,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(認真po)土瓜灣南亞童黨問題","createTime":"2019-03-18T08:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T15:04:44.000Z","uid":241224,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"02381dfd163721160c577aaf35bd8b945e6c06ab","tid":1066990,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ny86InDjdYc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNy86InDjdYc&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=3563c7bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ny86InDjdYc</a><br />\n<br />\n依家有班蝻童黨喺球場搞9人<br />\n諗住霸番個球場黎用<br />\n歡迎黎討論方法<br />\n或者黎幫手<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到兩個Plan<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cec6tKD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCec6tKD.jpg&h=ea1b4437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlan A B 就係人地挑機就打9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlan C 就係人地挑機由佢挑<br />\n我會帶cam<br />\n一過界就㩒住佢唔畀走然後報警<br />\n長期keep住咁做<br />\n並使用人海戰術搞旺個場<br />\n直至趕走班蝻<br />\n<br />\n兩個plan都好大機會有身體碰撞<br />\n因為佢地當正自己係肥屍<br />\n黎幫手既請做好心理準備<br />\n幫手既入tg<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/tkwfootball\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftkwfootball&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M9MQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=d023d19d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/tkwfootball</a>"},{"pid":"a420739eca05f9f485bec08353d34351462a9da2","tid":1066990,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"樓主成日係土瓜灣踢波?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4253b8a2ec4acd4af31cc35a450080f426a4436c","tid":1066990,"uid":241224,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"a420739eca05f9f485bec08353d34351462a9da2","tid":1066990,"uid":119783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T08:55:04.000Z","msg":"樓主成日係